&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take ambiguous, high-impact problems and drive them from idea to production.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Product and Design to define scope, trade-offs, and execution plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, build, and evolve production systems with a strong focus on reliability, correctness, and maintainability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance speed and quality, knowing when to move fast and when to slow down.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share ownership of the systems you build, including on-call responsibilities and incident response.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to technical and product decisions that shape the direction of your team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help raise the bar for how the team builds by improving standards, tooling, and processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
